text:
Ah, Nanakusa-chan!
Today's recording was really great!

Thanks to the thorough meeting we had last time!
We followed through exactly as planned.

It's rewarding to hear that! Oh, here's a treat!
Well then, let's work together again soon!

Yes, please do! Thank you again!
I'll enjoy this juice!

Hey, Nichika!
Sorry I couldn't attend the recording.

It's totally fine!
It ended in a flash.

I see…
Huh? What's with the two bottles you're holding?

I got these from the director.
Maybe they want me to mix them…?
